'''Century''' is an [[Wikipedia:imprint|imprint]] of [[Random House]] Publishers Group. They are responsible for Random House's hardback ''[[Star Wars]]'' fiction publications in the [[Wikipedia:United Kingdom|United Kingdom]]. Paperback publications are handled by [[Arrow Books Ltd.]], and factual books, such as ''[[The Making of Star Wars Revenge of the Sith]]'', are published under the [[Ebury Press]] label.

